profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.
products:

services:

profile:
Pillar To Post is a full service home inspection company dedicated to delivering a professional service within the London and St. Thomas area. 

Every Pillar to Post franchise is independently owned and operated. 

We provide thorough home inspection and our report is printed on site.

Pillar To Post is the “go-to” company for evaluations regarding the integrity and safety of the home as a whole. We are the professionals you call, not only at the time of the home transaction, but also for services related to home health and safety as you continue to live there. Pillar To Post is a benevolent home “GP”. You can trust your Pillar To Post home inspector to help you learn how to keep your home safe, healthy and green.

Visit me at http://troysimmersvanhevel.pillartopost.com/
Or follow me on Facebook https://www.facebook.com/pillartopostlondon
